The paper discusses document clustering and similarity measures, which are common topics in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of external thesauruses like WordNet and topic maps suggests a focus on knowledge representation and semantic analysis, which are also relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.DL).
